Show a summary per file</summary>\n\n| File | Description |\r\n| ---- | ----------- |\r\n| scripts/generate_otlp_projection.py | Adjusts generated decoder docs and gates the reference decoder behind `cfg(test)`. |\r\n| crates/ffwd-runtime/src/pipeline/submit.rs | Uses `Reject` for `PermanentError`; documents inflight metric drift on early returns. |\r\n| crates/ffwd-runtime/src/pipeline/run.rs | Documents terminal behavior (abandon queued batches) and unbounded `held_tickets` growth. |\r\n| crates/ffwd-io/src/tail/reader.rs | Documents unbounded `evicted_offsets` growth under rapid rotation. |\r\n| crates/ffwd-core/src/structural.rs | Adds comments explaining `try_into()` invariants for fixed-size blocks. |\r\n| crates/ffwd-core/src/scan_predicate.rs | Adds a comment clarifying the `len()==1` invariant before `expect`. |\r\n| crates/ffwd-core/src/json_scanner.rs | Adds comments clarifying invariants around 64-byte block handling. |\n</details>\n\n\n\n\n","commit_id":"b35db0308b79735ab1f8c44cd26d65a46505a62c","state":"commented","html_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2728#pullrequestreview-4186267155","pull_request_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/pulls/2728","_links":{"html":{"href":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2728#pullrequestreview-4186267155"},"pull_request":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/pulls/2728"}},"submitted_at":"2026-04-28T06:12:23Z","updated_at":"2026-04-28T06:12:23Z","author_association":"NONE"},"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/pulls/2728","id":3594036681,"node_id":"PR_kwDORzg8fM7WOKXJ","html_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2728","diff_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2728.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2728.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/issues/2728","number":2728,"state":"open","locked":false,"title":"Fix Permanen